Structure
=========

bootstrap.py             - zc.buildout bootstrap file.
build.sh                 - Building script for buildout.
buildout.cfg             - The main buildout config file.
README                   - This file.
INSTALL                  - General Installation instructions.
docs/AUTHORS             - Authors List.
docs/HACKING             - Hacking VMController.
docs/LICENSE             - The BSD (Simplified) license.
scripts/                 - Folders containing script to build, release, clean
src/                     - The root source folder
src/vmcontroller.common/ - VMController's common module.
src/vmcontroller.host/   - VMController's host module.
